<p align="center"><em>'following a government lead on a political timetable is an abandonment of independent &amp; creative &amp; critical thinking - &amp; there was never a time when students &amp; clients needed all three'</em><em style="cursor:auto"><!--NO CSS-->&nbsp;</em></p>
<p align="center"><em>'careers workers can each most usefully askof what is set out here - thinking, factors, dynamics and lives - "which most suggests a priority for action in my work?" - what's the answer?</em><em style="cursor:auto"><!--NO CSS-->&nbsp;</em></p>
